  }, {
    "tStartMs": 19920,
    "dDurationMs": 1969,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Yeah, exactly. Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21889,
    "dDurationMs": 2102,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But which came first?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 23991,
    "dDurationMs": 1902,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Well, \"The Drama\" first,\nobviously."
