  }, {
    "tStartMs": 97831,
    "dDurationMs": 1135,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then I'd jump back\ninto \"Spider-Man.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 98966,
    "dDurationMs": 1835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it was like --\nAnd then I just came"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 100801,
    "dDurationMs": 2235,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "literally the day\nI wrapped \"Euphoria,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 103036,
    "dDurationMs": 1802,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it was like four in the morning"
