  }, {
    "tStartMs": 106373,
    "dDurationMs": 1702,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to go to Budapest\nto shoot \"Dune.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 108075,
    "dDurationMs": 2536,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I was like, pack\nmy whole life up in one night."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 110611,
    "dDurationMs": 1768,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I was like, \"Let's go!\"\n-Let's go for it."
