  }, {
    "tStartMs": 155189,
    "dDurationMs": 1301,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when you were on \"Batman.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 156490,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm like, \"No,\nthat's just not true.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 157991,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-It is! It literally is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 160160,
    "dDurationMs": 2736,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Okay, so we have a friend --\nWe have a friend in common."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162896,
    "dDurationMs": 2569,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And they were FaceTiming\nwhile I was shooting \"Euphoria,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 165465,
    "dDurationMs": 1936,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but he was in --\nhe was in Batman mode."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 167401,
    "dDurationMs": 2202,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Ah.\n-And so I think he didn't--"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 169603,
    "dDurationMs": 1401,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Did I have the cowl on?\n-You were in character."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 171004,
    "dDurationMs": 1735,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-You had the the smokey eye."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 172739,
    "dDurationMs": 1535,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You had the whole thing.\n-Okay, okay, okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 174274,
    "dDurationMs": 2803,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-And I was like --\nAnd I was like, \"Hey!\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 177077,
    "dDurationMs": 1535,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you were like--\n-[Deep voice] \"Hi.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 178612,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "[ Laughter ]"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180113,
    "dDurationMs": 1435,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-I don't even think --\nI literally don't even--"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 181548,
    "dDurationMs": 1635,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-\"I'll call you later.\nI can't talk to you.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 183183,
    "dDurationMs": 2469,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "[ Laughter ]\n-\"I have to go fight crime.\""
