  }, {
    "tStartMs": 541341,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "He was asking me\nwhile we were shooting \"Dune\"..."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 543343,
    "dDurationMs": 2403,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-No!\n-...what I was, and I was like,\n\"I don't know yet."
