  }, {
    "tStartMs": 547648,
    "dDurationMs": 1768,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then when I came up with\nthe idea, he was like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 549416,
    "dDurationMs": 2202,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"You knew all along."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 551618,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you didn't tell me.\"\n-\"And you didn't tell me.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 553620,
    "dDurationMs": 1535,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-\"You didn't tell me.\"\nI was like --"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 555155,
    "dDurationMs": 1769,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Ah, I love it.\nI love you guys together."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 556924,
    "dDurationMs": 1601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Hopefully there's more\nand more and more films"
